- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper discusses the decidability of quantifier-free formulas.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) could be a possible category as the paper deals with functions and sets.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) could be a possible category as the paper deals with the syntax and semantics of a first-order language.
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) could also be a possible category as the paper deals with the manipulation of symbols in a first-order language.
